parameters: \n<Goat> What do we have here? It seems we have a lost fairy with no Calyx. Eating you will
\n<Fairy> Get your ugly face away from me! Do not make me turn your face into something
much uglier than it already is! Take this!!!
\n<Fairy> ....hahaha... I did not mean to punch you in the face Mr.Handsome demon...
\n<Goat> This is what happens when you offend the great Baphomet!
\n<Baphomet> Did you think you can actually escape with you life. You are as good as dead.
\n<Baphomet> What is this? That face, that hair, that armor.. I see a Calyx.
Eating you will greatly increase my power!
\n<Baphomet> Noooo! How can this be!?, me the Great Baphomet defeated by a mere Calyx!
\n<Baphomet> How can this be!?, me the Great Baphomet defeated by a mere Calyx!?
\n<\n[1]> I can feel a strange new power swelling within me.
You can now use the skill Energy Beam!
\n<Fairy> Looks like you were able to take some of Baphomet's Essence and made it your own.
You can probably use his abilities now.
\n<Fairy> Thanks for the help! Though it would have been better if you came to the rescue
\n<Fairy> If you came by any later, little beautiful me would have been dead.
\n<\n[1]> Sorry, but i do not really have the time to chit chat with you.
I have to head out to Home Point to see why I was summoned in this world.
\n<Fairy> Excuse me!? You should be lucky you met up with a beautiful lady such as myself.
I am the great and beautiful Silvia.
\n<Silvia> A Calyx like you should be happy you have come across a Sprite.
Sprites rarely show up in front of you Calyxs let alone someone who's not even special.
\n<\n[1]> For a lil sprite you sure do talk alot.
\n<Silvia> Grrr! Do not make me punch you in the face!
\n<\n[1]> Next time I think I will let you get eaten. Come'on let's go!
